description: NNDSS - Table IV. Tuberculosis - 2014.This Table includes total number of cases reported in the United States, by region and by states, in accordance with the current method of displaying MMWR data. Data on United States will exclude counts from US territories. Footnote:C.N.M.I.: Commonwealth of Northern Mariana Islands. U: Unavailable. -: No reported cases. N: Not reportable. NN: Not Nationally Notifiable Cum: Cumulative year-to-date counts. Min: Minimum. Max: Maximum. * Case counts for reporting year 2013 and 2014 are provisional and subject to change. For further information on interpretation of these data, see http://wwwn.cdc.gov/nndss/document/ProvisionalNationaNotifiableDiseasesS... Updated reports to the National Center for HIV/AIDS, Viral Hepatitis, STD and TB Prevention. Data for TB are displayed quarterly.
